irc;i, kh&ocirc;ng bị bột hay v&oacute;n cục v&agrave; tạo cảm gi&aacute;c mướt mịn thoải m&aacute;i</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tạo hiệu ứng đ&ocirc;i m&ocirc;i mịn l&igrave; tự nhi&ecirc;n v&agrave; mềm mịn</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Độ b&aacute;m m&agrave;u tốt, giữ m&agrave;u l&acirc;u trong thời gian d&agrave;i</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Bảng m&agrave;u son đa dạng, gồm 10 m&agrave;u son với sắc đỏ v&agrave; cam chủ đạo, trong đ&oacute;: Red Muse đỏ cam, Holy Chic đỏ hồng lạnh, Speak To Me n&acirc;u đỏ đất, Smoke Pink hồng san h&ocirc;, Murmuring hồng nude, Kind &amp; Love cam nude, Warming Wear cam vỏ qu&yacute;t, Focus On Me cam san h&ocirc;, Giving Pleasure cam gạch v&agrave; Over It cam ch&aacute;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.cocolux.com/2021/09/images/products/1633315580892-son-thoi-3ce-soft-matte-lipstick-3.jpeg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hiện tại Nula Cosmetic&nbsp;c&oacute; c&aacute;c m&agrave;u sau:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Focus On Me:&nbsp;</strong>Cam san h&ocirc;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.cocolux.com/2021/09/images/products/1633315379431-son-thoi-3ce-soft-matte-lipstick-focus-on-me-4.jpeg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.cocolux.com/2021/09/images/products/1633315379449-son-thoi-3ce-soft-matte-lipstick-focus-on-me-3.jpeg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.cocolux.com/2021/09/images/products/1633315379497-son-thoi-3ce-soft-matte-lipstick-focus-on-me-2.jpeg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.cocolux.com/2021/09/images/products/1633315379520-son-thoi-3ce-soft-matte-lipstick-focus-on-me-1.jpeg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Giving Pleasure:&nbsp;</strong>M&agrave;u cam gạch</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.cocolux.com/2021/11/images/products/1635908867276-son-thoi-3ce-soft-matte-lipstick-giving-pleasure.jpeg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.cocolux.com/2021/09/images/products/1633315426171-son-thoi-3ce-soft-matte-lipstick-gi