.jpeg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dung t&iacute;ch:</strong>&nbsp;30-50-80ml</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Thương hiệu:&nbsp;</strong>Jean Paul Gaultier</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Xuất xứ:</strong>&nbsp;Ph&aacute;p</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Nước hoa ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng</strong></em></p>', null);
